'''Lili Bonic''' neɣ (Boniche), acennay adzayri uday mucaɛen aṭas iluled g [[1921]] g [[Taqṣebt]] n [[Dzayer tamanaght|Dzayer]] (Kasba) yemmut ass n [[6 meɣres]] [[2008]] g [[Pari]] g [[Fransa]] ycennu [[aẓewan aɛrab-andalusi]] yecennu daɣen [[Ccaɛbi]], [[Rrumba]], s [[taɛrabt tadzayrit]] d tarumit, ccna ines imeẓẓwi (ḥammlent meden)
yceyɛit babas win yellan argaz uẓewan ula d netta, bac aken a d yeɣar ɣur aselmad [[Saɛud awahrani]] Ccix n uẓawen, yekcem daɣen g iɣerbazen n uẓuwen imucaɛen azal [[Mutribiya]] d [[Musiliya]]
yefkayas anemhal n [[Rradio n Dzzayer]] (Radio-Alger) adisider tadwilt n [[Ḥawzi]] ass imi yella yesɛa 15 isegwasen gelɛamris 

gar tuɣac ines llan : 

1- ana el warqa el meskina

2- il y a un seul dieu (yuen rebbi y gellan)

3- Bambino

